From: AX6600 Firmware <noreply@ax6600.local>
Subject: [PATCH] netdata: disable cloud/aclk to fix protobuf/absl compat

Disable Netdata Cloud (ACLK) feature to avoid protobuf/absl API
incompatibility. The aclk module uses deprecated protobuf APIs
that are incompatible with newer absl versions.

Error: no matching function for call to
'absl::lts_20240722::log_internal::LogMessageFatal::LogMessageFatal(...)'

Signed-off-by: AX6600 Firmware <noreply@ax6600.local>

--- a/Makefile
+++ b/Makefile
@@ -44,6 +44,7 @@ CONFIGURE_ARGS += \
 	--disable-ebpf \
 	--without-libcap \
 	--disable-dbengine \
+	--disable-cloud \
 	--disable-compression \
 	--disable-plugin-nfacct \
 	--disable-plugin-freeipmi \
